This paper deals with optimization algorithms for machine learning, which is a topic that falls under the category of "Machine Learning" (cs.LG). This suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the sub-categories of "Numerical Analysis" (cs.NA) and "Data Structures and Algorithms" (cs.DS).
